title: Willy and the Kate Fleming Case
Willy Saves Harvey from Fraud
description: The library fund for Renfrew, New Hampshire, is accidentally spent on a fund for a skyscraper in New York City. Willy must find a way to rectify the mistake and save Harvey from going to jail for fraud.
